cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY

The paper proposes a new algorithm for imitation learning that can learn interpretable and meaningful representations of complex behavioral data, including visual demonstrations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper applies the proposed method to the driving domain, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY).
